### Send File Message
POST http://localhost:5000/message-api/file-message
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZjhjOWJhYmY1NzU0YjQ5MjJiODVkNCIsImVtYWlsIjoidXNlcjFAbWFpbC5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiVVNFUiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NzkxNjIwNywiZXhwIjoxNzc4MDAyNjA3fQ.E5Nm4h0M7EEuGyBJP_bKRzWSQHACELrRWekEuCSWPBY
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ChatBoundary

--ChatBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="workspace"

69f8cc87bf5754b4922b85d6
--ChatBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="channel"

69f8cf70bf5754b4922b85f1
--ChatBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="messageType"

CHANNEL
--ChatBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Shared a file
--ChatBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./sample.png
--ChatBoundary--


